               <id root="1f53e672-406b-4c97-a985-bfef47e97ac0"/>
               <code code="34089-3" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="DESCRIPTION SECTION"/>
               <title>
                  <content styleCode="bold">DESCRIPTION</content>
               </title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Each round, green, peppermint flavored tablet, for sublingual administration contains:</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Hyoscyamine Sulfate, USP …… 0.125 mg.</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Hyoscyamine sulfate is one of the principal anticholinergic/ antispasmodic components of belladonna alkaloids.</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>
                     <renderMultiMedia referencedObject="MM1"/>
                  </paragraph>
                  <paragraph styleCode="Caption">(C <sub>17</sub>H <sub>23</sub>NO <sub>3</sub>) <sub>2</sub>• H <sub>2</sub>SO <sub>4</sub>• 2H <sub>2</sub>O M.W. = 712.85</paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20241115"/>
            </section>
         </component>
         <component>
